  "title_full": "AN ACT ESTABLISHING THE SCIENCE FOR CHANGE PROGRAM",
  "title_short": "",
  "abstract": "Seeks to expand the following Science and Technology programs of DOST: a. Health Self Sufficiency; b. Renewable Energy; c. Nuclear Science for Energy, Health, Agriculture and Industry; d. Climate and Environment Sciences; e. Food and Nutrition; f. Agricultural Productivity; g. Biotechnology for Industry, Agriculture, Health and Environment; h. Techology Business Incubation; i. Foreign Scholarship for STI; j. Promotion of Cutulture of Science.  Provides for new programs as follows:  Human Security R&d; Regional Infrastructure ((R&D Centers), facilities, HRD and R&D funding; Space Technology and ICT Dev't; S&T for Creative/Tourism/Services Industries; Artificial Intelligence: From HRD to R&D to Industry.\r\n\r\n",
